title: S16 Ep152: Supernatural News/Parashare: Get Your Tongue Off The TV Please Edition
itunes:title: Supernatural News/Parashare: Get Your Tongue Off The TV Please Edition
description:
Darkness Radio presents Supernatural News/ParaShare: Get Your Tongue Off The TV Edition with our special guest, Beer City Bruiser from Ring of Honor Wrestling!

We are just a few days shy of 2022 and the strangeness hasn't stopped!  So, we brought back our friend, Beer City Bruiser from Ring of Honor Wrestling to sort out the madcap stories of the week! A haunted pub has a spirit that threatens to kill people! A newly launched telescope may have all the answers to life in the universe, and a Japanese scientist wants to bring taste to your TV, and get you to lick your screen!
